!!!
%html{lang: "en"}
  %head
    %meta{charset: "UTF-8"}/
    %meta{content: "width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0", name:"viewport"}/
    %title Alocity 
    %link{rel: "stylesheet", href:"assets/css/bootstrap.min.css"}/
    %link{rel: "stylesheet", href:"assets/css/main.css"}/
    %link{rel: "stylesheet", href:"assets/css/company.css"}/
    %link{rel: "stylesheet", href:"assets/css/slick.css"}/
    %link{rel: "stylesheet", href:"assets/css/slick-theme.css"}/
  %body
    .main-banner
      .main-banner__content
        .main-banner__item
          .main-banner__img
            %img{ :src => "assets/img/company/bg.png"}/
          .main-banner__container
            .row
              .col-lg-6.col-md-6.col-12
                .main-banner__boxtext
                  .main-banner__text.main-banner__text--company
                    .main-banner__title.main-banner__title--company
                      %h1.title-company Our Mission
                      %span.subtitle-company A Smarter, Safer, Connected World
                    .main-banner__description.main-banner__description--company
                      %p We are set out to make our customer's lives more simple and secure by offering unprecedented visibility and control over their doors and facilities. Our solutions are designed to efficiently manage door access control, video surveillance, sensors, lighting, climate, & any IoT device with artificial intelligence & automation all from one place.
              .col-lg-6.col-md-6.col-12
                
                .main-banner__imags
                  .main-banner__imags--one
                    %img{ :src => "assets/img/company/image_3@3x.png"}/
                  .main-banner__imags--two
                    %img{ :src => "assets/img/company/image_4@3x.png"}/
        .main-banner__item
          .main-banner__img
            %img{ :src => "assets/img/company/bg.png"}/
          .container.main-banner__container
            .row
              .col-lg-6.col-md-6.col-sm-6
                .main-banner__boxtext
                  .main-banner__text.main-banner__text--company
                    .main-banner__title.main-banner__title--company
                      %h1.title-company Our Mission
                      %span.subtitle-company A Smarter, Safer, Connected World
                    .main-banner__description.main-banner__description--company
                      %p We are set out to make our customer's lives more simple and secure by offering unprecedented visibility and control over their doors and facilities. Our solutions are designed to efficiently manage door access control, video surveillance, sensors, lighting, climate, & any IoT device with artificial intelligence & automation all from one place.
              .col-lg-6.col-md-6.col-sm-6
                
                .main-banner__imags
                  .main-banner__imags--one
                    %img{ :src => "assets/img/company/image_3@3x.png"}/
                  .main-banner__imags--two
                    %img{ :src => "assets/img/company/image_4@3x.png"}/
    .main-company
      
      .row
        .col-lg-6.p-0.col-order
          .main-company__content
            .main-company__item
              .main-company__box
                .main-users__boximg.active
                  .main-users__img
                    %img{ :src => "assets/img/company/key-3.png"}/
                  
                .main-company__title
                  %p It all starts at securing the door
                .main-company__description
                  %p At AlocityÂ®, we believe that the door isn't just about keeping unauthorized people out. It's also about letting the right people in - at the right times, on the right terms, with the ability to manage anytime, from anywhere.
        .col-lg-6.p-0.col-order
          .main-company__boximg
            .main-company__img
              %img{ :src => "assets/img/company/bg_2.png"}/
            .main-company__imgs
              .main-company__imgs--one
                %img{ :src => "assets/img/company/image.png"}/
              .main-company__imgs--two
                %img{ :src => "assets/img/company/puerta-2.png"}/
        .col-lg-6.p-0.col-order
          .main-company__boximg
            .main-company__img
              %img{ :src => "assets/img/company/bg_2.png"}/
            .main-company__imgs
              .main-company__imgs--one.main-company__imgs--pad
                %img{ :src => "assets/img/company/image_2.png"}/
        .col-lg-6.p-0.col-order
          .main-company__content
            .main-company__item
              .main-company__box
                .main-users__boximg.active
                  .main-users__img
                    %img{ :src => "assets/img/company/key-3.png"}/
                  
                .main-company__title
                  %p Frictionless entry
                .main-company__description
                  %p Goodbye keys and cards. A quick-touch of a finger, or a glance at the face recognition reader is all you need to gain secure & instant entry into the smart-office or smart-home.
        .col-lg-6.p-0.col-order
          .main-company__content
            .main-company__item
              .main-company__box
                .main-users__boximg.active
                  .main-users__img
                    %img{ :src => "assets/img/company/key-3.png"}/
                .main-company__title
                  %p Smarter, Safer, Connected
                .main-company__description
                  %p We're on a mission to create a safer and connected world, with apps, systems, and devices all working together with artificial intelligence and automation all from one centralized platform.
        .col-lg-6.p-0.col-order
          .main-company__boximg
            .main-company__img
              %img{ :src => "assets/img/company/bg_2.png"}/
            .main-company__imgs
              .main-company__imgs--one
                %img{ :src => "assets/img/company/4.png"}/



              
   
    

      
